name: Killer Bean
description: Killer Bean Fan Token is a community-created meme token on the Ethereum blockchain inspired by the Killer Bean franchise. It gives fans a decentralized way to celebrate the cult-classic character known for his action-packed adventures and lasting impact on internet culture. The token has a renounced contract for permanent security, burned liquidity to maintain stability, and a deflationary supply that decreases with every transaction. It has no official affiliation with the original creator and is designed for collectors, enthusiasts, and community engagement.
